sions</h2>\n        <p>We are always on the lookout for exciting new manuscripts. If you have a story that you believe will captivate readers, we encourage you to explore our submission guidelines on our website. We champion original voices and believe in the collaborative process of bringing a book to life.</p>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View Guidelines</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p>Have a question, a comment, or interested in our latest releases? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n        <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@crimsonquill.com\" style=\"color: #960018;\">info@crimsonquill.com</a></p>\n        <p>Address: 123 Quill Lane, Literary City, LC 45678</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Quill Publishing. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}